{
  "stem": "142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Two in the United States, one in Rome, and one in-- I think, in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we are gone, you know, I don't think anybody-- anybody can tell that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know that somebody was there, and that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I-- we are only eyewitness of the final solution.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's why it's very important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's why I went-- you know, a few weeks ago, I just came back from Poland, you know-- with the young people that are hungry of knowledge what was going on for the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- the SS told us to search every-- everything that was coming in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had the facility to take anything and put it aside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, also, one of our members, a Greek guy by the name of Cohen, you know, that used to extract the gold teeth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, they-- when-- when it happened that we know we are not going to survive, and we wanted to do something-- an uprising, a revolution, you know-- that was some things we were sending-- the partisans were about 30 miles away from us.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not too cooperative with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But just we were sending money to them, and they were sending knives, dynamite to be able to-- to do something one day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through parties.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there's always means. you know, people-- with money, you can do anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- the Germans were every day taking them away, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You put it in a-- in a can, whatever it was, and they will take them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was listening the other day that, in Switzerland, all this-- I don't know if you see last week-- all that gold belongs to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
